    <div class="about-us-container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>
            Welcome to <strong>BookFinder</strong>! Our mission is to make it easier for book lovers around the world to find information on their favorite books, authors, and genres. Whether you're a casual reader or a literary enthusiast, we aim to provide an easy and enjoyable experience.
        </p>

        <h2>What We Do</h2>
        <p>
            At BookFinder, we connect users with the Open Book API to search for books, authors, and their works. Simply enter a book title, and we'll fetch the results directly from one of the largest open databases of book records. With access to millions of books across a wide variety of genres, you're bound to find what you're looking for.
        </p>

        <h2>Key Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Fast and Accurate Search:</strong> Instantly search for books using our intuitive interface, powered by the Open Book API.</li>
            <li><strong>Comprehensive Information:</strong> Find book titles, author details, and even book cover images to help you identify the right book.</li>
            <li><strong>Responsive Design:</strong> Our platform is optimized for use across devices, whether you're on a desktop, tablet, or mobile phone.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
            Our goal is to democratize access to book information, providing a platform for readers to explore literature from all corners of the globe. We are passionate about reading, and we want to help you discover your next great read.
        </p>

        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Completely free to use.</li>
            <li>Access to millions of books, from classic literature to modern bestsellers.</li>
            <li>Easy-to-use interface for book search and browsing.</li>
            <li>Direct book data from Open Library, ensuring up-to-date and accurate information.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>
            Have questions or feedback? We'd love to hear from you! Feel free to reach out to us at <strong>support@bookfinder.com</strong> for any inquiries or suggestions.
        </p>
    </div>
